msgid "TXT_RANDOM_PGUARD_10"
msgstr ""
"If there is any honour inside that pathetic shell of a body, you'll enter into the arms of the Order."

#, fuzzy
msgid "TXT_ILOG103"
msgstr "Just when I think we've seen it all! They go in human and come out... I don't even want to think about it. Destroy this horror!"

msgid "TXT_SPEAKER_MACIL_S_ADVISOR"
msgstr "Macil's Adviser"

msgid "TXT_SPEAKER_ADVISOR"
msgstr "Adviser"

msgid "TXT_SPEAKER_ARMORER"
msgstr "Armourer"

#, fuzzy
msgid "TXT_BBSUB_SCRIPT17_D13644_OHWEL"
msgstr "Hmm. No fuss, no muss, nothing for mum to clean up... Get me one, please.\n"

msgid "TXT_DLG_SCRIPT04_D21224_BUSIN"
msgstr "Business my arse. Help, guards, I've got a live one."

msgid "TXT_DLG_SCRIPT04_D46996_YEAHR"
msgstr "Yeah, right. OK, get your arse to work."

msgid "TXT_DLG_SCRIPT05_D0_HALTN"
msgstr ""
"Halt. No one gets through here without authorisation from the Warden or the Governor."

msgid "TXT_DLG_SCRIPT06_D24256_WHATS"
msgstr ""
"What's your clearance? There's no unauthorised personnel allowed up here."

#, fuzzy
msgid "TXT_DLG_SCRIPT06_D10612_GOODL"
msgstr "Good luck. I've opened several of our tunnels for you. It should make your task easier. Oh, size ten, perfect! ...But dreadful colours."

msgid "TXT_DLG_SCRIPT10_D25772_WELLI"
msgstr ""
"Well, I'm back up to my old tricks again, I'm still working on your implants. Did you know that Macil has now authorised them for everyone? No, huh? It's because you turned out so well. Anything I can do for you?"

msgid "TXT_DLG_SCRIPT17_D13644_OHWEL"
msgstr ""
"Oh well, word has it that the bailey's warehouse received a shipment of maulers, that's the weapon that vaporises."

#, fuzzy
msgid "TXT_DLG_SCRIPT22_D3032_ITSAT"
msgstr "It's a top secret area. Not only is the Order breeding some kind of... creature in there, I've seen with my own eyes a strange artifact called a Talisman. nobody's allowed near it. Rumour is that it holds great power if united with two others of its kind."

msgid "TXT_ILOG28"
msgstr ""
"We're looking for Weran, who calls himself the Rat King. I'm sure it's descriptive as well as colourful."

msgid "TXT_ILOG1102"
msgstr "Find the Governor's mansion and talk to the Governor to get your reward"

msgid "TXT_SUB_INTRO6"
msgstr ""
"But there are whispers of discontent. If we organise, can we defeat our masters? Weapons are being stolen, soldiers are being trained. A movement is born: born of lifelong strife!"

#, fuzzy
msgid "TXT_SUB_MAP03_4"
msgstr "...the Programmer: creator of the AI which controls the Acolytes. Destroy the Programmer, and we may cripple the Order's troops with a single blow. But caution: we have reports he can vaporise attackers."

msgid "TXT_SUB_LOG28"
msgstr ""
"We're looking for Weran, who calls himself the Rat King. I'm sure it's descriptive as well as colourful."

msgid "TXT_SUB_LOG23"
msgstr ""
"Word from the boss is stand back when you whack the crystal, or else you'll end up mesquite-flavoured too."

