msgid "TXT_DLG_SCRIPT04_D12128_PASSY"
msgstr "Pass your ID through here for access."

msgid "TXT_ILOG14"
msgstr ""
"OK, \"Trust no one\" is the name of the game! Let's get that prison pass from the Governor. Take the broken coupling to him."

msgid "TXT_ILOG1009"
msgstr ""
"Use the pass Mourel gave you to get into the prison. Once inside, talk to Warden Montag. Find a way to free the prisoners."

msgid "TXT_SUB_LOG14"
msgstr ""
"OK, \"Trust no one\" is the name of the game! Let's get that pass from the Governor and free those prisoners."

msgid "TXT_SUB_LOG36"
msgstr "That brick… Didn't we pass that brick? No…"

